## API Endpoints

{{- if or (eq .ServiceType "auth") (eq .ServiceType "both")}}

### Authentication

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/register` | Register new user |
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/login` | Login and get tokens |
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/refresh` | Refresh access token |
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/logout` | Logout and invalidate session |
| GET | `/api/v1/auth/user` | Get current user |
| PUT | `/api/v1/auth/user` | Update user profile |
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/user/password` | Change password |

{{- if .EnableMFA}}

### MFA

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/mfa/setup` | Initialize MFA setup |
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/mfa/verify` | Verify and enable MFA |
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/mfa/disable` | Disable MFA |
{{- end}}

{{- if .HasGDPR}}

### GDPR

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
{{- if .HasGDPRConsent}}
| GET | `/api/v1/auth/gdpr/consent` | Get active consents |
| PUT | `/api/v1/auth/gdpr/consent` | Update consent |
| GET | `/api/v1/auth/gdpr/consent/history` | Get consent history |
{{- end}}
{{- if .HasGDPRDataExport}}
| GET | `/api/v1/auth/gdpr/export` | Export all user data |
{{- end}}
{{- if .HasGDPRDataDeletion}}
| DELETE | `/api/v1/auth/gdpr/delete` | Delete account (right to erasure) |
{{- end}}
{{- end}}
{{- end}}

### Health

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/health` | Liveness probe |
| GET | `/ready` | Readiness probe |

## Security Considerations

### Production Checklist

- [ ] Enable HTTPS/TLS termination
- [ ] Set secure cookie flags (`Secure`, `HttpOnly`, `SameSite=Strict`)
- [ ] Configure CORS for your domains only
- [ ] Set up rate limiting thresholds
- [ ] Enable request size limits
- [ ] Configure allowed hosts
- [ ] Set up proper logging and monitoring
- [ ] Regular security updates
{{- if .HasGDPR}}
- [ ] Review GDPR data retention policies
- [ ] Set up data processing agreements with sub-processors
{{- end}}
{{- if .HasFrontend}}
- [ ] Update `VITE_API_URL` to production backend URL
{{- if .HasPostHog}}
- [ ] Configure PostHog for production (check data residency requirements)
{{- end}}
{{- if .HasSentry}}
- [ ] Configure Sentry DSN for production environment
- [ ] Set up release tracking and source maps
{{- end}}
{{- end}}

